  "description": {
   "en": "A new type of gambling tale written by Shinji Inakatsu, a rising star who suddenly came into the limelight with his shocking work ``Frankensteiner''!\n\nRyuichi, a boy who is an amateur at mahjong, decides to play mahjong against the novice killer \"K\" on the street, relying only on the tricks Araki taught him: \"Surikae\" and \"Nanataiko\"! Will Ryuichi be able to win? ?\n\nRyuichi is a hikikomori who is afraid to even face other people at the cash register at a convenience store, but before he knew it, he had developed the almost miraculous skill of shoplifting. One day, Ryuichi meets a man named Araki and is taken to a street mahjong venue in Marunouchi in the middle of the night..."
